author: Mr Naba
text:
Sahakari vaneko Nepal ko banking system ko Ra aartha tantra ko sabbai bhanda thulo loophole ho.

Euta sano kagaj ko vaar ma karadau Ra aarabau ko sampati tanidincha..

Anusandhan Garda Direct galat dekhiye pani.. Direct Karbahi garna ko lagi sahakari bivag lai kehi adhikar nai chaina!

Karan: sahakariko concept banking system haina.. tesh Karan yeshko chuttai kanun cha...
Tara bank jasto sahuliyat Ra total Kam garcha.. lasta Jane vaneko sahakari aain anusar jancha... Tyo kanun ma kunai solid kanun nai chaina... Dherai kamjor kanun cha sahakari aain ko...

Sahakari concept ma rini vhanney kurai hudaina... Tara practical ma sahu Ra rini vannae kuro practice garcha!

Time time ma sahakari aain lai tight garne koshish gariyo.. Tara lasta uhi...

Kanun ma sahakarile maximum 20 lakh Vanda beshi Rin dinu namilne banaunu parcha.. 20 lakh Vanda beshi ko karobar ma rastra bank bata approval linu parne.. ra 20 lakh Vanda mathi ko karobar ma rastra bank niyaman nikaya hune ho vane... Ra banking aain le Pani aakarshit hune banaune ho vane dherai Kura balance huncha..

Natra, aarulai k Dosh dine hajur... Hami aafai vitra virus vaneko yehi sahakari system ko wrong practice nai ho!
